import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import "./styles/GrowthTable.css"; const GrowthTable = ({ character, gameClass, expertise, starsphere }) => { const starsphereGrowths = starsphere? 15 : 0; const expertiseGrowths = { hp: expertise? gameClass.hp : 0, str: expertise? gameClass.str : 0, mag: expertise? gameClass.mag : 0, dex: expertise? gameClass.dex : 0, spd: expertise? gameClass.spd : 0, def: expertise? gameClass.def : 0, res: expertise? gameClass.res : 0, lck: expertise? gameClass.lck : 0, bld: expertise? gameClass.bld : 0, } const growthTotals = { hp: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, str: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, mag: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, dex: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, spd: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, def: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, res: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, lck: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, bld: character.hp + gameClass.hp + starsphereGrowths + expertiseGrowths.hp, } return (
Character Stats Base Class Starsphere Expertise TOTAL

{character.name}

{gameClass.name}

 HP {character.hp} {gameClass.hp} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.hp} {growthTotals.hp}
STR {character.str} {gameClass.str} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.str} {growthTotals.str}
MAG {character.mag} {gameClass.mag} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.mag} {growthTotals.mag}
DEX {character.dex} {gameClass.dex} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.dex} {growthTotals.dex}
SPD {character.spd} {gameClass.spd} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.spd} {growthTotals.spd}
DEF {character.def} {gameClass.def} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.def} {growthTotals.def}
RES {character.res} {gameClass.res} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.res} {growthTotals.res}
LCK {character.lck} {gameClass.lck} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.lck} {growthTotals.lck}
BLD {character.bld} {gameClass.bld} {starsphereGrowths} {expertiseGrowths.bld} {growthTotals.bld}
) } export default GrowthTable;
